name: person_id
description: A foreign key identifier to the person for whom the data was recorded.

name: date
description: Date of the heart rate log.

name: zone_name
description: Name of the custom heart rate zone. The possible values for heart rate zone are: out of range, fat burn, cardio, and peak.

name: min_heart_rate
description: Minimum range for the custom heart rate zone.

name: max_heart_rate
description: Maximum range for the custom heart rate zone.

name: minute_in_zone
description: Number minutes within the specified heart rate zone.

name: src_id
description: Flag indicating the participant portal that this record originated from.
